snippet.textDisplay: It's one of my frvt coke studio performance ... I still remember watching it on TV and my grandfather dancing to it as Assamese music is also pahadi music and being a pahadi (gharwali) brought up in Maharashtra .. it was quite fascinating and seeing my grandfather dance to both the music still makes me smile... Music bring back memories to you ❤️😀
